OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782154094
OL,3,CUS-Iran establish 'communication line'
OL,4,Cfor Strait of Hormuz as talks resume
OL,6,FThe US and Iran have agreed to create
OL,7,Fa establish a "communication line" to
OL,8,Fensure safe passage of ships in the
OL,9,FStrait of Hormuz, as negotiators in
OL,10,FSwitzerland prepare to continue talks
OL,11,Ffor the second day.
OL,13,FMediators Qatar and Pakistan hailed
OL,14,Fwhat they called "encouraging
OL,15,Fprogress" in a joint statement, noting
OL,16,Fthat both sides had also agreed to
OL,17,Festablish a "de-confliction cell" to
OL,18,Fensure the "termination of military
OL,19,Foperations in Lebanon".
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@bO]
