OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782154094
OL,3,CUS-Iran establish 'communication line'
OL,4,Cfor Strait of Hormuz as talks resume
OL,6,F"Tireless Pakistani and Qatari
OL,7,Fmediation has delivered major progress
OL,8,Fto end Lebanon War," Iranian Foreign
OL,9,FMinister Seyed Abbas Araghchi said as
OL,10,Fhe reshared the statement on X.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
