PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782154094
OL,3,CUS-Iran establish 'communication line'
OL,4,Cfor Strait of Hormuz as talks resume
OL,6,F"Oil and petrochem exports are waived,
OL,7,Fblockade lifted, some frozen assets
OL,8,Freleased, and major reconstruction and
OL,9,Fdevelopment plan launched for Iran.
OL,10,F(First) real test: Lebanon
OL,11,Fdeconfliction cell."
OL,13,FA senior US diplomat also said there
OL,14,Fhad been progress on multiple fronts,
OL,15,Fincluding the establishment of
OL,16,F"mechanisms" to ensure the Strait of
OL,17,FHormuz, a vital waterway which sees
OL,18,Fthe passage of a fifth of the world's
OL,19,Foil, remains open.
