PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782154094
OL,3,CUS-Iran establish 'communication line'
OL,4,Cfor Strait of Hormuz as talks resume
OL,6,FChief negotiators for the US include
OL,7,FJD Vance, the vice president, special
OL,8,Fenvoy Steve Witkoff and Jared Kushner,
OL,9,Fthe son-in-law of the president, while
OL,10,FIran is represented by parliamentary
OL,11,Fspeaker Mohammad Bagher and Araghchi.
OL,13,FThe first day of the talks on Sunday
OL,14,Fwas nearly blighted by US President
OL,15,FDonald Trump, who spoke to reporters
OL,16,Fand fired off comments on Truth Social
OL,17,Fthat offended the Iranians.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
