PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782154094
OL,3,CUS-Iran establish 'communication line'
OL,4,Cfor Strait of Hormuz as talks resume
OL,6,FReports of Iranian President Masoud
OL,7,FPezeshkian stating he would "never
OL,8,Fback down from the right to enrich
OL,9,Furanium," led Trump to tell Fox News
OL,10,FPezeshkian should watch what he says
OL,11,Fand also threaten to take over Iran,
OL,12,Faccording to the channel's
OL,13,Fcorrespondents.
OL,15,FThe president also wrote online: "Iran
OL,16,Fmust immediately stop their highly
OL,17,Fpaid PROXIES in Lebanon from causing
OL,18,Ftrouble. If they don't, we'll hit Iran
OL,19,Fvery hard again, just like we did last
OL,20,Fweek, only harder!!!"
OL,26,@oD@]OUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
