PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782154094
OL,3,CUS-Iran establish 'communication line'
OL,4,Cfor Strait of Hormuz as talks resume
OL,6,FThe talks were then paused due to the
OL,7,F"publication of an insulting message
OL,8,Fby the US president", with Iran's
OL,9,Fdelegation leaving the negotiating
OL,10,Fsite, according to Iranian state media.
OL,12,FThe interim deal to end the fighting
OL,13,Fin Iran, signed last week, outlines a
OL,14,F60-day period for negotiators to end
OL,15,Fthe war, which began on February 28.
OL,17,FIran has put addressing the fighting
OL,18,Fin Lebanon high on the agenda, and
OL,19,Fclosed the Strait of Hormuz again on
OL,20,FSaturday following continued exchanges
OL,21,Fof fire between Israel and Hezbollah.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
