OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782154094
OL,3,CUS-Iran establish 'communication line'
OL,4,Cfor Strait of Hormuz as talks resume
OL,6,FA renewed ceasefire in Lebanon from
OL,7,FSaturday now appears to be holding,
OL,8,Fand Israel's military has said it will
OL,9,Flift movement restrictions for
OL,10,Fresidents near the Israel-Lebanon
OL,11,Fborder on Monday morning.
OL,13,FNeither Israel nor Hezbollah is a
OL,14,Fsignatory to the US-Iran deal.
OL,16,FMore than 4,000 people in Lebanon have
OL,17,Fbeen killed in Israeli strikes since
OL,18,Fthe latest Israel-Hezbollah war began
OL,19,Fin March, two days after the conflict
OL,20,Fin Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
